    - rid: 2042809308283404365
      type: {class: ChoiceNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-1
        text: While you investigate the strange looking tree you see what looks like
          a paper in the corner of your eye.
        choices:
        - choiceText: you pick up the paper and read it
          nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-2
        - choiceText: "you ignore the paper, it probably isn\u2019t important anyway
            right?"
          nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-4
    - rid: 2042809308283404366
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-2
        text: Reading the paper you quickly notice that its an old news paper. In
          the news paper you read about a hero that did a heroic act.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-3
    - rid: 2042809308283404367
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-3
        text: You can't make out who the hero was, because for some reason the name
          and face of the hero are crossed out.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-4
    - rid: 2042809308283404368
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-4
        text: 'You look at closer at the palm tree and realise it has clues carved
          into it for your next objective. '
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-5
    - rid: 2042809312053297226
      type: {class: StartQuestNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest1-5
        text: It looks like an anvil next to a rock.
